# Group Campaigns/ConnectionTypes
ConnectionTypes can be accessed and updated here.

## ConnectionTypes Collection [/campaigns/:id/connectionTypes/?include=includes]
Get all ConnectionTypes that are part of a Campaign 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Campaign to perform action with. Has example value.

