## ConnectionType [/campaigns/:id/connectionType/:subid/?include=includes]
Get a ConnectionTypes that is associated with a Campaign 
+ Parameters
    + id (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the Campaign to perform action with. Has example value.
    + subid (required, number, `1`) ... Numeric `id` of the ConnectionType to perform action with. Has example value.

### Retrieve a ConnectionType [GET]
+ Response 200 (application/json)

